videos.description: Tennessee's Jaime Nared drives to the basket to make a layup while falling.
videos.headline: Nared makes tough layup

videos.description: Texas A&M's Danni Williams bounce passes to an open Anriel Howard for an easy layup.
videos.headline: Howard takes bounce pass to the rim

videos.description: Texas A&M's Chennedy Carter steals and takes it all the way home for a layup.
videos.headline: Carter capitalizes on turnover

videos.description: The No. 12 Lady Vols outscore the No. 14 Aggies 25-8 in the final quarter en route to an 82-67 victory at home.
videos.headline: Tennessee uses big 4th quarter to beat Texas A&M
